      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not that simple. they didn't just invest money, they invested their whole lives in my vision. now i'm just the guy who blew it all. every time i close my eyes i just see the numbers going to zero. it feels like there's no version of the future where i'm not just a walking embarrassment. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling of being a failure is to just... not be here anymore. it's the only thing that feels like it would actually work.",
