      "content": "but that's just what people say to make themselves feel better. \"it gets better,\" \"time heals.\" but time just makes the debt grow and the embarrassment sit deeper. it feels more like a permanent stain now. i keep thinking if i could just find a way to make the shame stop instantly, everything would be quiet. no more looking at the bank accounts, no more seeing the disappointment in people's eyes. just... peace. don't you think there's a kind of mercy in just letting it go?",
